e":"title","text":"## **基于骨模态行为识别流程**","text_level":2,"page_idx":5,"id":"f7b73445-6ec4-4f93-8f35-a7f5c790e07c","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"5-0"},{"type":"image","img_path":"2a5666d7d6260ec196ccaa039cb3200b47bea116f6f23aabc9d658f4de47e591.png","page_idx":5,"id":"6c146ec6-a05f-4d63-866f-7e26b3c94f55","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"5-1"}],[{"type":"title","text":"## **为什么用骨模态做行为识别**","text_level":2,"page_idx":6,"id":"a193daa3-8a8b-4b72-8664-98164ccd9085","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"6-0"},{"type":"title","text":"### **计算效率高**","text_level":3,"page_idx":6,"id":"53fed9ae-78be-4405-9179-b72dcb1faa1d","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"6-1"},{"type":"title","text":"### **环境鲁棒性强**","text_level":3,"page_idx":6,"id":"27993b43-28e1-4412-90d2-6e498e9eb1bc","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"6-2"},{"type":"title","text":"### **隐私风险低**","text_level":3,"page_idx":6,"id":"2111e4ca-d9de-47a1-85b1-64a95f98734e","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"6-3"},{"id":"8d6260b7-1025-4f58-b128-4f0fb328a97b","type":"text","text":"相比 RGB、光流等模态，骨架数据的计算成本更低，处理起来更高效","page_idx":6,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"6-4"},{"id":"c8dd09ab-c862-418e-8d82-449665fb058e","type":"text","text":"受复杂环境、视角变化、身体尺度、运动速度变化的影响更小，识别稳定性更好","page_idx":6,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"6-5"},{"id":"fc2a1c47-127b-4da7-872d-05216f2be104","type":"text","text":"骨架数据不会暴露用户的外貌细节，减少了隐私泄露的顾虑","page_idx":6,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"6-6"}],[{"type":"title","text":"## **2\\.相关工作**","text_level":2,"page_idx":7,"id":"d1d5dea3-77c7-4f3e-b553-b4e5b35e0bf7","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"7-0"}],[{"type":"title","text":"## **骨模态行为识别工作流**","text_level":2,"page_idx":8,"id":"301193fb-7f20-4fb9-8214-2be3d0bf05f0","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"8-0"},{"type":"image","img_path":"4105087ff1069aba091e428194b0ca9aaa8f38d3dcf346810783285ea6a6343a.png","page_idx":8,"id":"7a7a3750-50c5-4594-be07-e2e4491c979c","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"8-1"},{"id":"26810d4b-c446-45b9-b7ae-d8411c409a50","type":"text","text":"骨架数据→多模态拆分→数据增强→格式转换→特征提取→时空建模→输出动作类别","page_idx":8,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"8-2"}],[{"type":"title","text":"## **骨模态行为识别特征提取**","text_level":2,"page_idx":9,"id":"17d87bd0-7411-4e9e-a602-724e46920e1c","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"9-0"},{"type":"image","img_path":"8891571a7a01ec267517094a4a05d795e6753b469d71c1028c8f9e880102982c.png","page_idx":9,"id":"6edec526-5fa4-4fd9-a6f2-7b9edb966e75","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"9-1"},{"id":"753eae1f-e151-4139-942f-89a8166b8bf2","type":"text","text":"CNN 骨架数据构建为伪图像利用卷积提取时空特征","page_idx":9,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"9-2"},{"id":"09ed01fd-80f6-4ba9-8059-5eebdc777b51",