e_idx":10,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"10-5"}],[{"type":"title","text":"## **GCN 骨模态行为识别研究现状**","text_level":2,"page_idx":11,"id":"bb3d3f11-9485-4aee-b60e-31ddf360e6b7","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"11-0"},{"id":"c7333ef0-d334-49dd-b0d5-85bcb2ea657b","type":"text","text":"**邻接矩阵**","page_idx":11,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"11-1"},{"id":"90bf13b9-1836-4983-b82c-1ba70729c5dc","type":"text","text":"**相对位置编码**","page_idx":11,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"11-2"},{"id":"c9fd3c41-9792-4e4b-bb2f-28a3686b4c00","type":"text","text":"**多关系建模**","page_idx":11,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"11-3"},{"id":"6f8bfff0-f01a-4c2e-8837-d8b64c303ffe","type":"text","text":"固定拓扑：基于骨骼物理连接定义固定的邻接矩阵","page_idx":11,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"11-4"},{"id":"c7ee510e-ea46-4065-9253-bbe64ae272a3","type":"text","text":"可学习拓扑：捕捉物理连接和非连接关节间的关系","page_idx":11,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"11-5"},{"id":"fa1e7c8b-707a-42c0-889c-f9441fe29426","type":"text","text":"存在\"灾难性遗忘\"问题：骨骼拓扑信息在训练中逐渐被侵蚀","page_idx":11,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"11-6"},{"id":"87ad6416-195e-4d8f-9f2c-d6b538b34b16","type":"text","text":"在 NLP 和 CV 被证明有效","page_idx":11,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"11-7"},{"id":"04f5c106-600b-4836-91eb-aa4880615a0f","type":"text","text":"对图数据上的Transformer模型有益","page_idx":11,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"11-8"},{"id":"a6d04f25-7c9c-4387-8a20-c809203f2b36","type":"text","text":"但在骨架动作识别领域探索不充分","page_idx":11,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"11-9"},{"id":"333c8a87-7347-45a6-ad02-cd9a083dc3d1","type":"text","text":"每层并行使用多个GC","page_idx":11,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"11-10"},{"id":"81c0a993-d747-489f-beec-34de594fa36f","type":"text","text":"引入注意力机制调整连接权重","page_idx":11,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"11-11"},{"id":"58ceb88b-86ca-4edb-b88d-68fd60fb39eb","type":"text","text":"计算开销大，参数量大，低效","page_idx":11,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"11-12"}],[{"type":"title","text":"## **3\\.现存问题**","text_level":2,"page_idx":12,"id":"a09f1e48-7295-4316-8478-c52081070555","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"12-0"}],[{"type":"title","text":"## **GCN 问题一：“灾难性遗忘”**","text_level":2,"page_idx":13,"id":"f63daa8f-2822-4307-91f4-09287aff4d29","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"13-0"},{"type":"image","img_path":"8cfc743543cdbc6ea2c381c0756948773ee5f3cad8b2b1457c002f33ed6ac26c.png","page_idx":13,"id":"1b8d7e7b-30b2-4db9-b5b6-6c2289b81d16","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"13-1"},{"id":"bfa5a9e8-0f01-4af5-899a-59a2e9ccf0d7","type":"text","text":"训练前初始化的是符合人体物理结构的骨骼拓扑，但训练结束后，原始的骨骼连接性没有被保留下来，即“灾难性遗忘”","page_idx":13,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"13-2"}],[{"type":"title","text":"## **GCN 问题二：“低效多关系建模”**","text_level":2,"page_idx":14,"id":"f3a133de-533a-4a75-becc-2684e717afc2","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"14-0"},{"type":"image","img_path":"dc120d4b87f5b89518a20f8da9e2bfbbbfd94092812db95a1c9208716785f976.png","page_idx":14,"id":"b657f0d1-3e7d-4793-9fc4-25d0f15db0b0","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"14-1"},{"id":"bb46df2f-4917-4255-9825-0692d08b3313","type":"text","text":"“低效多关系建模”：参数和计算量大，权重矩阵存在大量冗余","page_idx":14,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"14-2"}],[{"type":"title","text":"## **4\\.研究方法**","text_level":2,"page_idx":15,"id":"484dbf0c-f092-4d99-a0d0-eefe5b1daf0d","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"15-0"}],[{"type":"title","text":"## **BlockGC 模块**","text_level":2,"page_idx":16,"id":"414f22ab-8cf7-43a6-9553-10466bd202d3","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"16-0"},{"type":"image","img_path":"ab32f923567445a166a58c46f1187a7633921ebec35cbce2ba480ecf636db483.png","page_idx":16,"id":"1544ffd8-7947-4341-8740-feeab34792a1","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"16-1"},{"id":"7332ec1c-858d-49f6-9337-24a1e0a0c60e","type":"text","text":"包括拓扑编码（保留骨架结构信息）和分块对角卷积（降低参数量）","page_idx":16,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"16-2"}],[{"type":"title","text":"## **静态拓扑编码**","text_level":2,"page_idx":17,"id":"5f134831-887f-4783-8adb-ae34240b0f30","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"17-0"},{"type":"image","img_path":"7964f8e3a6964325508cbd687fc36ced5bd4ca8b060cb4e8e5d899f629b00118.png","page_idx":17,"id":"c34f456a-7816-4410-808e-5ea7ad280566","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"17-1"},{"type":"image","img_path":"3ec61439564d586a6b59e98c9ae8b6cf2e17a87e28454382b124cc870af122c8.png","page_idx":17,"id":"0195dbfb-7095-4616-82ad-c627011c33db","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"17-2"},{"id":"a8c5d207-8e48-436f-9e6a-0076b3c2d33a","type":"text","text":"采用骨骼最短路径距离（SPD），通过嵌入表转换成可学习的特征向量，构建出静态拓扑编码矩阵 B，保留物理连接","page_idx":17,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"17-3"}],[{"type":"title","text":"## **动态拓扑编码**","text_level":2,"page_idx":18,"id":"de23fc91-0ecb-44f3-9723-a53372263134","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"18-0"},{"type":"image","img_path":"a43f96b27a41eae4030f8ac99a64d4ece92412ccd2d58a400e4a1612f83a89ca.png","page_idx":18,"id":"bfe8d1a8-5d48-422c-ad05-c591972882ef","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"18-1"},{"id":"990b7de9-66c1-4d84-87b8-58998bb2e5ab","type":"text","text":"基于关节间欧氏距离构建骨架的过滤序列，提取出随动作变化的拓扑条形码，再通过向量化和投影，得到动作特有的动态拓扑特征","page_idx":18,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"18-2"}],[{"type":"title","text":"## **动态拓扑编码**","text_level":2,"page_idx":19,"id":"e4301abd-455d-4c31-bf88-e0a26df51fd2","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"19-0"},{"id":"427ca80a-1b82-48b2-866d-3b6b64b70186","type":"text","text":"梳头","page_idx":19,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"19-1"},{"id":"9f105d98-850e-4cff-ae57-2156c406b134","type":"text","text":"握手","page_idx":19,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"19-2"},{"type":"image","img_path":"7f9f3f3d628a804751ca9f48c5a5beea84a3c0ff189dea86b4cb5dc2f77cba83.png","page_idx":19,"id":"53334e72-fecd-4d44-b9d2-af36f7639991","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"19-3"},{"id":"790e05cb-9f27-457e-93dc-0e0acacd26f7","type":"text","text":"各组样本呈现出明显的类间差异、类内相似特性","page_idx":19,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"19-4"}],[{"type":"title","text":"## **分块对角卷积**","text_level":2,"page_idx":20,"id":"e994d249-142b-40b0-9c6f-315d71bd3817","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"20-0"},{"type":"image","img_path":"27fffb4829180b007f4b23231959ea7a0cd91971060e14f4f044ac6e3f445690.png","page_idx":20,"id":"01dcc2fb-0066-4ea3-8f5f-22a826cc9e72","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"20-1"},{"type":"image","img_path":"7d82fdabe0a3925c935185f6a9cc92300fb13df7a668fba3c011a4a04d44a9ce.png","page_idx":20,"id":"43c07ae4-5dc2-4b73-be9c-54b62d1752d5","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"20-2"},{"id":"f7ce3898-fb9b-436e-a696-56981ec224b2","type":"text","text":"Ensemble of GCs：最朴素的多关系方法，直接堆叠 K 个完全独立的 GC 层","page_idx":20,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"20-3"},{"id":"57c41705-87f6-43fa-98f5-c8d4543cda13","type":"text","text":"Proposed BlockGC：K 个邻接矩阵 \\+ K 个独立的分块对角权重矩阵","page_idx":20,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"20-4"},{"type":"image","img_path":"4600c763053bf9106dd7342e574b668a9def1630e106a082b5113688d34f03d9.png","page_idx":20,"id":"25ea60fd-765a-472b-a319-2fb408347776","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"20-5"}],[{"type":"title","text":"## **分块对角卷积推导**","text_level":2,"page_idx":21,"id":"a6463ac8-1e05-4b92-b3bd-3c2475270314","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"21-0"},{"type":"image","img_path":"449ddc31a5487954037e706becb2ef5fb03b363b09529b9a2d4cea0bdd409048.png","page_idx":21,"id":"1be80c99-6210-4699-90b1-01da07524da3","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"21-1"}],[{"type":"title","text":"## **分块对角卷积优势**","text_level":2,"page_idx":22,"id":"7ef0d6cc-0277-4184-8ef7-a2698b572c3c","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"22-0"},{"type":"image","img_path":"108c05f195ddab39882d5ddcc3d69bc0eeb615b09c24d650b81d8791d4ef0cd2.png","page_idx":22,"id":"2bc865dc-2d4f-4722-816b-a7cb7f6d8e23","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"22-1"}],[{"type":"title","text":"## **BlockGCN 架构**","text_level":2,"page_idx":23,"id":"8a5d08fa-0b89-4f4b-a1af-504007eb90fa","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"23-0"},{"type":"image","img_path":"e478da0a006819c4f1419de4bb8304d3548ac5369bd00661cc558ba04765d192.png","page_idx":23,"id":"280af0fa-2d45-4a47-bbf3-437be4511761","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"23-1"},{"id":"98518008-886a-4e55-8e5b-8148d6d8f5b8","type":"text","text":"多帧骨架序列→BlockGC→多尺度时间卷积","page_idx":23,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"23-2"},{"id":"754494ad-fd97-4820-a5ce-49061e51dbbd","type":"text","text":"→全局平均池化→全连接层→Softmax","page_idx":23,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"23-3"}],[{"type":"title","text":"## **5\\.实验结果**","text_level":2,"page_idx":24,"id":"9a945962-8e49-418b-ba8a-bd17fd6c8c47","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"24-0"}],[{"type":"title","text":"## **对比实验**","text_level":2,"page_idx":25,"id":"959e346a-20ed-4ca7-8144-c7a10962e409","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"25-0"},{"type":"image","img_path":"c77c181223e40921247e11ec52174c3ab6a540ed96bcbaee0c4fa761fb433518.png","page_idx":25,"id":"bf80b34b-482c-4416-afbf-7442848370c9","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"25-1"},{"id":"81c0f51d-35f0-42b6-a7a6-d8a87de4b51a","type":"text","text":"可见该方法不仅在性能上领先，而且在参数量和计算量上都具备优势","page_idx":25,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"25-2"}],[{"type":"title","text":"## **消融实验1**","text_level":2,"page_idx":26,"id":"f7811435-1a2b-40a8-8dfe-46ca3c6ecc33","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"26-0"},{"type":"image","img_path":"dc5e0d122dbf0e5513bc1d35e343650d322bffa45ac1b019e6869074cb516a0d.png","page_idx":26,"id":"c48442ae-aac4-4f26-b18a-49dff35397ef","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"26-1"},{"id":"94bd5356-23e5-400b-867f-49ef083c04a9","type":"text","text":"验证模型对邻接矩阵不同初始化具备良好泛化能力，精度不会出现大幅波动。得益于分块卷积设计，单个邻接矩阵匹配专属分块权重矩阵，让模型自主高效学习关节拓扑关联","page_idx":26,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"26-2"}],[{"id":"23053aab-0ba3-4a26-8e5b-f2ee23f5dc25","type":"text","text":"**消融实验2**","page_idx":27,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"27-0"},{"type":"image","img_path":"739ec9a0da302e8466e01c0bb25790f9a1f49ee05207158747fe3d70c995ac6f.png","page_idx":27,"id":"7a31f8e0-7021-4b7c-bb3e-e6a5b148e1d5","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"27-1"},{"id":"7e8474d1-8880-4e07-a9f5-6afd77755d89","type":"text","text":"BlockGC 结合动态与静态拓扑编码后，模型准确率提升 1\\.7%，同时总参数量降低 38%","page_idx":27,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"27-2"}],[{"type":"title","text":"## **消融实验3**","text_level":2,"page_idx":28,"id":"abf47f0f-aef7-4c75-9fb3-d6ba3b26e176","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"28-0"},{"type":"image","img_path":"66420e1f284d3a2cf87b031b95def174070260423339692e23d4c3ce735edabe.png","page_idx":28,"id":"ee1e8eb3-d282-450b-96d7-6a57efbc44ba","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"28-1"},{"id":"65c84f3f-a183-44fa-8cb4-117fabf1f5b5","type":"text","text":"DecouplingGC 随分组数增加参数量膨胀、性能提升有限；","page_idx":28,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"28-2"},{"id":"a9ecba18-41bf-4242-9096-135156e708fb","type":"text","text":"而 BlockGC 在分组 Groups = 8 的时候，实现了参数量减半的同时准确率不降反升","page_idx":28,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"28-3"}],[{"type":"title","text":"## **6\\.总结**","text_level":2,"page_idx":29,"id":"b364a122-dd8c-4980-aeb7-44b86d7a731e","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"29-0"}],[{"id":"fac6321e-2355-4e42-a511-f235c38be523","type":"text","text":"问题解决：针对骨架动作识别中 GCN 模型存在的拓扑结构遗忘、多关系建模能力不足两大核心痛点，提出了拓扑编码与 BlockGC 模块","page_idx":30,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"30-0"},{"id":"3454120e-c9e5-47a5-8e00-b1c1a76f7e78","type":"text","text":"核心成果：BlockGCN 在主流基准上达到了当前最优性能，同时实现了识别精度与计算效率的双重提升","page_idx":30,"color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"30-1"}],[{"type":"title","text":"## **谢谢观看**","text_level":2,"page_idx":31,"id":"d4330c42-9770-488f-ab58-34b5aa0a8279","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_size":[595,842],"anchor":"","block_position":"31-0"}]],"mergeConnections":[]}